data.Title: Scotiabank North Tower - Bay Adelaide Centre
121 King Street
data.Description: Located in the heart of Toronto’s financial district, this 540,000 square foot Class A office building is close to the corner of King and Bay Street with direct access to the path. This 25 storey office tower is recently renovated and LEED EB Gold and BOMA BEST Gold. The property has a roster of quality tenants and is well-served by a variety of retail amenities and transportation options.
